data.description: Conveniently situated just a few minutes away from Main Street in Highlands, this wonderful residence offers ample space for the entire family, thoughtfully designed to provide a comfortable separation between sleeping quarters. Welcoming guests at the front is a charming water fountain. The living room features a floor-to-ceiling fireplace that not only defines the space but also creates a cozy atmosphere, while the adjacent dining room is graced by a second fireplace, adding a touch of romance. Flowing from the dining area is a generously sized covered screened porch, an idyllic spot to relish the refreshing mountain breeze.   The kitchen has been beautifully renovated, showcasing new cabinetry, top-notch Viking appliances, and elegant granite countertops. A unique tin ceiling adds a dash of character. The expansive master bedroom boasts a wall of windows that invite natural light, complemented by a well-appointed closet. The master bathroom is a luxurious retreat, highlighted by a Maya Tub steam shower.  Ascending upstairs, you'll find two bedrooms accompanied by a shared bathroom. The terrace level of the home encompasses a compact kitchen, an office space, and an additional master suite featuring another indulgent Maya Tub steam shower. This level also houses a bonus room, a spacious storage area, and a private entrance.
